## Content pillars (rotate across the week)

1. **The Star** — the four-pointed-star mark as a recurring hero motif: logo animations, the star "appearing" over destinations, light/lens-flare moments. Builds mark recognition. (~2/wk)
2. **Wanderlust** — dreamy Malaysian + outbound travel visuals (cinematic, scroll-stopping). Attracts the travel audience and signals the category softly. (~2/wk)
3. **Cryptic line** — one-line bilingual teasers over visuals: *"Soon, finding your trip won't feel like this."* / *"Voya. Tunggu."* Intrigue without explanation. (~1/wk)
4. **Engagement bait** — "What do you think Voya is?" polls, guess-in-comments, this-or-that destinations. Feeds the algorithm + builds community. (~1/wk)
5. **Relatable travel feeling** — light, shareable micro-moments (the joy/chaos of planning a trip), brand kept vague. Shareability engine. (~1/wk)

