## Prerequisites (before content goes live)

1. **Secure handles + create accounts** — confirm `@voya` (or agreed handle) on TikTok, Instagram, Facebook are claimed and the business accounts are set up. *(Flagged as a blocker in `Voya/Branding/voya_strategy_c.md` §12.)*
2. **Link-in-bio waitlist** — a simple "Voya is coming — join the list" landing page (email capture only, no product detail) so teaser attention converts to an owned audience. This is the one measurable conversion goal of the teaser.
3. **Brand asset kit for Higgsfield** — confirm the logo file, exact hex codes, and DM fonts are ready so every generated asset is on-brand.

